One-shot recovery script. Polls gluetun's Docker HEALTHCHECK in a loop (up to 120s) and restarts all dependent containers (qBittorrent, SABnzbd, Prowlarr, Radarr, Sonarr, Audioarr, Readarr, Jellyseerr) once the VPN tunnel is confirmed healthy. Uses a lock file to prevent concurrent runs. Called automatically by gluetun-vpn-monitor or run manually.
